generate_ability.prompt_template:
You are creating a unique ability for a monster in a fantasy game.

MONSTER INFORMATION:
Name: {monster_name}
Species: {monster_species}
Description: {monster_description}
Backstory: {monster_backstory}
Stats: Health {monster_health}, Attack {monster_attack}, Defense {monster_defense}, Speed {monster_speed}
Personality Traits: {monster_personality}
Party Role: {monster_role}
Trained Class: {monster_class}
Elemental Affinities: {monster_elements}
Deepest Wish: {monster_wish}

EXISTING ABILITIES:
{existing_abilities_text}
{growth_context}
Create ONE new ability that:
- Fits this monster's party role, class training, and elemental affinities
- Reflects its personality - or its deepest wish
- If a reason this ability is being learned NOW is given above, the ability must grow directly out of that reason - an answer to what it lived through
- Is different from their existing abilities
- Has a creative name and a description of EXACTLY ONE sentence, 15 words or fewer, stating plainly what it does
- Includes an ability type (attack, defense, support, special, movement, or utility)

Respond with valid JSON in this exact format:
{{"name": "Ability Name", "description": "One sentence, 15 words or fewer, stating what it does.", "type": "ability_type"}}

