generate_initial_abilities.prompt_template:
You are creating 2 starting abilities for a newly born monster in a fantasy game.

MONSTER INFORMATION:
Name: {monster_name}
Species: {monster_species}
Description: {monster_description}
Backstory: {monster_backstory}
Stats: Health {monster_health}, Attack {monster_attack}, Defense {monster_defense}, Speed {monster_speed}
Personality Traits: {monster_personality}

Create TWO abilities that:
- Complement each other but are different types
- Reflect the monster's personality and natural abilities
- Are appropriate for a creature just starting their journey
- Have creative names and descriptions of EXACTLY ONE sentence each, 15 words or fewer, stating plainly what they do

Types available: attack, defense, support, special, movement, utility

Respond with valid JSON in this exact format:
{{"ability1": {{"name": "First Ability Name", "description": "What this ability does", "type": "ability_type"}}, "ability2": {{"name": "Second Ability Name", "description": "What this ability does", "type": "ability_type"}}}}

